WEBVTT

00:02.532 --> 00:05.733
She has no identification,
no wallet, keys,

00:05.853 --> 00:07.683
and she wouldn't talk to the cops.

00:07.751 --> 00:09.854
So they dropped her on our doorstep?

00:09.922 --> 00:12.140
When I was on the force,
we used to do that all the time.

00:12.260 --> 00:15.933
Involuntary psychiatric hold.

00:16.001 --> 00:18.603
You know, we cut out
a lot of paperwork.

00:21.739 --> 00:22.873
Wait here.

00:22.941 --> 00:24.074
You got it.

00:27.176 --> 00:29.212
What's your name?

00:29.279 --> 00:32.183
I hear you caused
quite a disturbance tonight.

00:32.252 --> 00:36.689
Some anti-Semitic remark
set you off.

00:36.756 --> 00:38.623
They made a joke.

00:38.691 --> 00:40.958
The businessmen at the bar.

00:41.026 --> 00:43.860
They said,
"Don't let them Jew you down."

00:43.928 --> 00:45.418
That's how it always starts, you know?

00:45.526 --> 00:47.360
With jokes.

00:47.427 --> 00:49.328
There's blood on your coat there.

00:49.396 --> 00:50.763
Is it yours?
It's theirs.

00:50.831 --> 00:52.399
I broke a beer bottle.
I stabbed them.

00:52.466 --> 00:54.400
They will live, but...

00:54.468 --> 00:56.470
they will never forget.

00:56.538 --> 00:58.272
I'm not immune

00:58.340 --> 01:00.307
to the atrocities
your people suffered.

01:00.375 --> 01:03.311
Did you lose someone in the war?

