We'll start treatment
first thing in the morning.

01:16.393 --> 01:17.852
Lock her up.

01:36.093 --> 01:37.822
Am I going to die?

01:38.555 --> 01:40.188
Not exactly.

01:40.256 --> 01:41.923
As a matter of fact,

01:41.991 --> 01:44.692
after this, you'll
probably live forever.

